dmca.title: Blogger DMCA Complaint- Randy Souther
dmca.body:
March 19, 2007
 
Dear Blogger Legal Support, 
I am writing to notify you of copyrighted material appearing on your site without permission.

1.
The material being infringed upon is an article titled "Dylan at 60," written by Joyce Carol Oates, and located here:
 
http://jco.usfca.edu/ondylan.html
 
I have permission from the author to reprint her material on my web site.
